===Etymology===
{{L.}} [[legumen]], [[pulse]]

===Proper noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''''Leguminosae'''''
#{{botany}} a [[botanical name]] at the rank of [[family]]. The ''Leguminosae'' is the family that has a [[legume]] as its fruit: [[circumscription]] of the family is stable. Note that the ''[[ICBN]]'' allows the name ''[[Fabaceae]]'' to be used as an alternate for this name, but that the circumscription of ''Fabaceae'' is not stable.  

